text: Nordovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Nordovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,000 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 40 km from Meleuz. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Nordovka
